{"tid":801823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國防部研港澳居民可否參軍","createTime":"2018-09-01T03:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T13:30:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c7e96e700a10ce9594cea081a3eed84aae1532","tid":801823,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:36:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180901/20489396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F20489396&d=rPgQoPP2bU%2BhQE9jxV%2FwA6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4e78abcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F20489396&h=4c8260fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180901/20489396</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月01日 <br />\n<br />\n國防部研港澳居民可否參軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180901/large/a0803a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180901%2Flarge%2Fa0803a.gif&h=9e4bf2fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國防部指正研究論證港澳居民是否可以參軍入伍的問題。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本學年入讀北京清華大學的港澳新生，首次要接受強制性軍訓，令人關注有關措施未來會否擴展至全國。國防部新聞發言人吳謙表示，香港回歸以來「一些香港同胞表達出參軍入伍、為國防事業貢獻力量的意願」，有關方面正研究論證港澳居民是否可以參軍入伍的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n清華港澳新生需強制軍訓<br />\n<br />\n開學前夕，清華大學本科新生中的392名「新生骨幹」，上月18日提前到校參加為期3天的訓練營，當中包括近60名港澳台學生。與往年港澳地區學生自願參加新生軍訓不同，今年清華要求所有港澳新生也和其他同學一起參加軍訓，但台灣學生仍是自願參加。<br />\n<br />\n內地高等學校多年來都強制新生入學後必須接受軍事訓練，時間由兩周至三周不等。其中清華大學的軍訓號稱「最苦」，長達22天，內容包括20公里的拉練、野營拉練、實彈射擊等項目。<br />\n<br />\n專收港澳台僑學生的廣州暨南大學，是全國少有不設軍訓的高校。民建聯的港區人大代表曾在3月兩會提案，要求中央讓港人享有更多國民待遇，包括設立渠道讓港人申請內地公務員職位、允許港人參軍。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘯軒  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n內地居住證式樣曝光<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n外交部官員列席《南早》編採會"},{"pid":"f9a44a0f4b1909100c81ea57a813c7f2eb6811df","tid":801823,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e646a92bed87d7d9182ac1bab219f8ae3f9a8856","tid":801823,"uid":25858,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"強制參軍去前線做炮灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0f32886aa1e3e750bff800b5170cd144a7ac1a","tid":801823,"uid":53026,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"新移民？巴基斯坦兵？"},{"pid":"1fb8daba8d025d6eab43a4bd07caef8542c8d873","tid":801823,"uid":29093,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"畀閪茶00後飲， 佢地做乜都肯架"},{"pid":"d842a5020dd9eabe9c647821e8b5e575a75a3046","tid":801823,"uid":61280,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強制參軍去前線做炮灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港豬有機做抗美援朝2.0大前線鳥！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歷屎會否重演，當年共狗送KMT降將著背心雪戰........<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4dc1ebc6c3688037a93f5b82fbe23171791ee0bb","tid":801823,"uid":985,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:51:23.000Z","msg":"如果參軍保證比層樓你係香港住過世，香港會有好多人參軍。"},{"pid":"48ec1b903e60080e6dab3fa2caeba04e1a61d18b","tid":801823,"uid":42283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"之後想邊個死直接徵兵就得了"},{"pid":"f4297aa35e191b4a9e9574e99c1e0f6c377ed895","tid":801823,"uid":143241,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03